    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"tough time\" though. this isn't something you just bounce back from. the debt is in the millions and the shame is permanent. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person who thought they could pull this off. there's no \"next chapter\" when you've burned every bridge. everything is just... finished.",
